overview.en: GSTT is a global diversified application eco-wallet based on blockchain technology and socially based on the GSTT Foundation. It is currently only distributed by official channels and is inseparable and does not support transactions.
overview.zh: GSTT 是 GSTT基金会旗下以区块链技术为基础，以社交为切入点的全球多元化应用生态钱包，目前仅由官方渠道发放，不可分割，不支持交易。
